txt.en: The Gaunt-lord Ivar, aided by a band of sellswords, swept through the village of Stoneheight in his search for his helm. When his goals were reached, he abandoned the village to the mercy of the sellswords.
Defeat Búbhosh-grat, and Dale Truitt within 10 seconds of each other.
You have defeated Búbhosh-grat, and Dale Truitt within the same moment.
